with the murder of Layla Briggs.

37:47.617 --> 37:49.608
This will.

37:54.697 --> 37:57.894
- No, Frank, you called Tucker.
- He called me.

37:57.937 --> 38:01.168
No, Frank, you called.
8:22. You called him.

38:01.217 --> 38:05.256
I told you, that was about a problem
with the Tennessee regulators.

38:05.297 --> 38:07.128
As soon as I got to the office,

38:07.177 --> 38:10.453
