on your assistant's thigh.

38:42.137 --> 38:45.652
Nasty is cheating old ladies
from Tennessee out of their savings.

38:46.737 --> 38:49.809
And choking the air
out of Layla Briggs' windpipe,

38:49.857 --> 38:53.736
