just massaging it really.

39:34.457 --> 39:37.767
She liked it but then her eyes said stop.

39:37.817 --> 39:41.412
- Stop? So why didn't he?
- Er. I don...

39:41.457 --> 39:44.733
Oh, I don't know.
He'll claim it was for my benefit.

39:44.777 --> 39:46.768
But the truth,

39:48.097 --> 39:50.816
the truth is,
that was the biggest turn-on for him.

39:50.857 --> 39:53.451
Not the sex part,

39:53.497 --> 39:56.057
the seeing how far you can go.

39:56.097 --> 39:58.372
And he went all the way.

39:58.417 --> 40:01.454
