40:13.497 --> 40:15.453
15, 16.

40:15.497 --> 40:18.534
- You and Frankie?
- Minors.

40:18.577 --> 40:22.650
Besides, it's just the way it was then.
Down there.

40:23.457 --> 40:27.211
